   Group Key: documentdb_api_internal.bson_expression_get(collection.document, '{ "" : "$city" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson)
   ->  Index Only Scan using city_rent_1 on documentdb_data.documents_9103 collection (actual rows=7 loops=1)
         Output: documentdb_api_internal.bson_expression_get(document, '{ "" : "$city" }'::bson, true, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson), document
